sed -i.bak "/gem ['\"]$g['\"].*, *$/ N; s/\n *//g; /gem ['\"]$g['\"]/ d" Gemfile
done

circle_yml.string:
## Customize the test machine
machine:
  services:
    - cassandra

  timezone:
    America/New_York

## Customize checkout
checkout:
  post:
    - git submodule sync
    - git submodule update --init # use submodules

## General Rules
# general:
  # branches:
    # ignore:
      # - master

## Customize dependencies
dependencies:
  cache_directories:
    - "~/dependency_cache"

  bundler:
    without: [osx]

  pre:
    - script/circle_ci/resolve_cassandra_dependency
    - script/circle_ci/resolve_phantomjs_dependency

  # Compute the assets once and cache them
  post:
    - RAILS_ENV=development bundle exec rake assets:precompile:
          timeout: 400

  # pre:
  # override:
  # we automatically cache and restore many dependencies between
  # builds. If you need to, you can add custom paths to cache:
  #
  # cache_directories:
    # - "custom_1"   # relative to the build directory
    # - "~/custom_2" # relative to the user's home directory

## Customize database setup
database:
  override:
    # replace Circle's generated database.yml
    - cp config/database.yml.ci config/database.yml
    - bundle exec rake db:create db:structure:load sunspot:solr:start --trace
    - bundle exec rake cassandra:structure:load --trace
    - bundle exec rake db:test:seed --trace
    - script/circle_ci/create_circle_databases

## Customize test commands
# test:
  # override:
    # - phpunit test/unit-tests # use PHPunit for testing
  # post:
    # - bundle exec rake jasmine:ci: # add an extra test type
        # environment:
          # RAILS_ENV: test
          # RACK_ENV: test

## Customize deployment commands
deployment:
  integration:
    branch: integration
    commands:
      - bundle exec autotag create ci
      - RAILS_ENV=development bundle exec rake integration deploy

  staging:
    branch: integration
    commands:
      - bundle exec rake integration deploy

  phrase_app:
    branch: phrase_app
    commands:
      - git config --global user.email "zephyr-dev@googlegroups.com"
      - git config --global user.name "Phrase App Bot"
      - git fetch
      - git checkout -f integration
      - git pull --rebase origin integration
      - git merge phrase_app --no-ff -m "Merging phrase_app updates"
      - git push origin integration

## Custom notifications
# notify:
  # webhooks:
    # # A list of hashes representing hooks. Only the url field is supported.
    # - url: https://someurl.com/hooks/circle
